00:34:41,873 --> 00:34:43,625
Look, you know she's gonna do it anyway.

420
00:34:44,458 --> 00:34:47,004
I'll just tell her nobody commented. Okay?

421
00:34:47,795 --> 00:34:49,840
You know what? I'm done.

422
00:34:51,382 --> 00:34:54,887
Lisko. I know that name.

