00:35:02,895 --> 00:35:05,063
Just couldn't let it go.

426
00:35:05,147 --> 00:35:07,608
I think that's why he got fired.

427
00:35:07,691 --> 00:35:11,320
He's always been--Well, he used to be like me.

428
00:35:11,945 --> 00:35:14,448
Can't let something gountil he figures it out.

429
00:35:16,992 --> 00:35:19,077
Well, I wonder if he lived here in '88.

430
00:35:19,995 --> 00:35:20,996
What do you mean?

431
00:35:21,788 --> 00:35:24,625
Well, it was before I came to town,but I heard about it.

432
00:35:25,292 --> 00:35:27,085
The mayor's kid went missing.

433
00:35:27,169 --> 00:35:28,837
His name was Richie Fife.

434
00:35:35,844 --> 00:35:39,014
<i>He was abducted one nightwhile he was riding his bike home.</i>

435
00:35:39,890 --> 00:35:41,850
<i>Everyone started locking their doors.</i>

436
00:35:41,934 --> 00:35:43,310
<i>People moved away.</i>

437
00:35:43,393 --> 00:35:45,437
<i>I mean,they caught the guy who did it, but...</i>

438
00:35:46,146 --> 00:35:48,899
<i>they never found outwhat happened to Richie.</i>

439
00:35:51,568 --> 00:35:53,237
What do the cops think happened?

440
00:35:54,738 --> 00:35:56,031
I don't know.

441
00:35:56,865 --> 00:36:00,494
They never released the file,and once it was in the past,

442
00:36:00,577 --> 00:36:03,539
folks around herewanted it to stay that way.

443
00:36:03,622 --> 00:36:05,958
Well, do you thinkthey caught the right guy?

444
00:36:12,381 --> 00:36:17,219
Actually, the person they arrestedfor Richie's murder...

445
00:36:19,096 --> 00:36:21,098
that was Penny Gillis's brother.

446
00:36:26,395 --> 00:36:27,396
Keep diggin'.

447
00:36:30,357 --> 00:36:34,069
Hey. Everything I said here...

448
00:36:34,736 --> 00:36:37,698
You do knowwhat an anonymous source is, right?

