00:36:43,078 --> 00:36:44,371
I won't quote you.

451
00:36:46,665 --> 00:36:48,000
Why are you helping me?

452
00:36:50,043 --> 00:36:52,713
I don't likewhen they pat me on the head either.

453
00:37:19,448 --> 00:37:20,449
Dad?

454
00:37:23,744 --> 00:37:24,745
Dad?

455
00:37:26,455 --> 00:37:27,664
Dad.

456
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:33,128
All right.

457
00:38:12,417 --> 00:38:15,045
Hey. Hey, what are you doing up?

458
00:38:15,128 --> 00:38:17,381
You told me there were no comments.

459
00:38:18,507 --> 00:38:19,925
Oh, sweetie.

460
00:38:20,509 --> 00:38:24,638
Look, I just didn't want youto get hurt, okay?

461
00:38:28,475 --> 00:38:30,394
But it-- it's so mean.

462
00:38:30,477 --> 00:38:33,522
Look, I know. I know, I know.

463
00:38:33,605 --> 00:38:36,275
Look, when people don't haveto say things to your face,

464
00:38:36,358 --> 00:38:40,153
like on the Internet, yeah,they can be really mean.

465
00:38:41,154 --> 00:38:42,281
All right?

466
00:38:44,324 --> 00:38:46,285
I was talking about you.

467
00:38:48,871 --> 00:38:51,039
I thought we didn't keep secrets.

468
00:40:17,501 --> 00:40:20,045
Oh, my God. How embarrassing.

469
00:40:29,429 --> 00:40:34,309
"This article, paper, or whatever it is,is so lame."

470
00:40:37,479 --> 00:40:40,732
"Go home. You're a loser."

471
00:40:47,739 --> 00:40:52,619
"Perhaps you're too young to understandthe words 'sensationalist' and 'trash.'"

472
00:40:53,370 --> 00:40:56,498
"Cute little girlsaren't supposed to be journalists.

473
00:40:56,582 --> 00:40:58,166
Stick to tea parties."

474
00:41:02,379 --> 00:41:03,380
Freak.

475
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:08,760
You're probablynever gonna talk to me again.

476
00:41:13,849 --> 00:41:17,519
"Keep it up. Maybe somedayyou'll write something intelligent."

477
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:19,771
"Maybe Hilde killed her."

478
00:41:21,148 --> 00:41:24,401
"See, this is whyyou shouldn't educate girls."

479
00:41:24,484 --> 00:41:26,695
"I hate whoever wrote this."

480
00:41:31,283 --> 00:41:33,994
"Who even let this little girlon the Internet?"

481
00:41:34,077 --> 00:41:36,663
"Hate to break it to you, but you suck."

482
00:41:37,414 --> 00:41:39,041
"You're ugly."

483
00:41:39,124 --> 00:41:40,959
Well, that felt off-topic.

484
00:41:45,714 --> 00:41:47,758
"You're just a stupid little girl.

485
00:41:47,841 --> 00:41:49,843
Why don't you learnto keep your mouth shut?"

486
00:41:49,927 --> 00:41:52,095
Excuse me, ladies.Do you want to sit down?

487
00:41:52,179 --> 00:41:54,139
A friend of mine once said

488
00:41:54,223 --> 00:41:58,644
that the best way to keep a secretis to pretend like there isn't one.

489
00:42:00,687 --> 00:42:05,108
Well, I thought she said it, but thenit turned out to be Margaret Atwood.

490
00:42:05,776 --> 00:42:09,613
I don't like secrets.And I don't like pretending.

